E1R2AUD.original: ~z~I ain't got no beef with you.
~z~I'm not letting you tell Ray I've got this money.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~我不会让你们告诉Ray钱在我手里的。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Always does, man. I hate museums. Wait for us.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~随叫随到，哥们。我讨厌博物馆。等着吧。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~I don't trust that Ray Boccino from the moment I saw him.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~我刚见到Ray Boccino就觉得他信不过。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~I wouldn't want this Niko Bellic coming for me. Guy is deranged.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~我可不想被Niko Belic这家伙追杀。这人太猛了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~That Ray has gone and sold us down the river.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~那个Ray已经跑了，他把我们都出卖了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Mr. Roth and Mr. Green have been waiting for ya, you mook.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~Roth先生和Green先生已经在等你了，蠢驴。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~I like you, Ray. Still keep your sense of humor in the face of an almighty fuck up. See you around.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~我喜欢你，Ray。虽然刚出了个大岔子，但你还是那么幽默。再见了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Shit. You don't wanna get in that Slav's way.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~操。可不想跟那个斯拉夫人作对。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~I got all the money that diamonds can buy.
~z~Anything for the Chapter, my brother, even pizza. We'll see you soon.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~为了帮派在所不辞，好兄弟，连披萨都得吃。咱们晚点见。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Nicky? Fuck, I mean Nicky, I didn't like the guy. But, hell, they don't normally come that cheap.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~Nicky？操，不是，Nicky？我不喜欢这人，但是这么便宜的杀手上哪儿找啊。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa. Since we're having a little show and tell, let's see some money.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~喔，喔，喔，喔。要我们给你验货可以，先把钱拿出来。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, boo fucking hoo. Where's the money? And don't you hang up on me. Don't you hang up on me...
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~是吗，关我屁事。老子钱呢？你别挂我电话，你别挂我电话啊...

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~You better not be pulling nothing, Johnny. Or I'll start pulling your fucking teeth. You hear me?
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~你最好别耍花招，Johnny。不然我让你脑袋开花，听到没？

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Uhh, yeah, this is Ray Boccino. Shut your mouth and don't say nothing incriminating on this uhh, voicemail.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~呃，对，我是Ray Boccino。管住嘴巴，别在电话留言里说什么违法的事。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~We're being set up. We're being screwed!
~z~Mind waiting here while I get the cash. All these tattoos might scare em.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~你们别动，我去拿钱。一群纹身男会吓死他们的。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~All you guineas are two faced pricks.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~你们意大利佬都是两面三刀的混蛋。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Okay, let's see the stuff, gentlemen. Mori, come over here.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~好了，先验一下货吧，先生们。Mori，你过来。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~That don't sound too salubrious, Jonathan. Ah fuck sign us up, brother.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~听上去就对身体不好，Johnathan。啊，算了，带上我们吧，兄弟。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Your services are needed, Clay. We're doing some Italian contract work.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~要你来干活了，Clay。有份意大利佬派的活。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~These bills ain't going back to Raymond.
~z~John John. Ashley sends her love, yeah.
~z~Uhh, brother man. I need some help. Shit's kicked off at the Libertonian.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~呃，兄弟，我需要帮忙。自由城博物馆闹翻天了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Terry, man, I could sure do with some help. Stuff went bad at the Libertonian.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~Terry哥们，我很需要有人帮忙。自由城博物馆出了状况。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Can you boys wait here while I get our money?
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~我拿钱的时候你们能等在这儿吗？

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~You didn't even need to open your mouth and shit got screwed. Pucchiacha.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~你不开口我都知道事情搞砸了。你个贱逼。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Once you start a job, you better finish it.
~z~Ah, Johnny boy. You got my cut?
~z~We worked hard for this cash, slick. It's Lost MC property.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~为了这钱我们累死累活，滑头。这是失落帮的财产。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Where's the fucking money, John? I'm getting anxious.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~你妈的老子的钱呢，John？我等不及了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Just make sure my man Nicky walks away with half the bread, buddy. Ciao.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~记得把一半的钱交给我的人Nicky，伙计。再见。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Shit. It's a motley crew we got here.
~z~uh, let's hope this goes a little better than before, yeah?
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~呃，希望这次能比上次顺利点，好吗？

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Come back here. Let's fucking talk about this.
~z~You start touching them exhibits. Shit. We're coming.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~你对展品下手了？妈的。我们来了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Awww, man. You mean I got to sit here with Terry. Shit.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~啊，哥们。那我只能和Terry坐着发呆。妈的。真无聊。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Whoa. Surpirse. You are a fuckin' ape. Who woulda guessed it.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~哇哦，太惊喜了。你没进化全是吧？真没想到啊。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Always does, man. I hate museums. Wait for us.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~随叫随到，哥们。我讨厌博物馆。等着吧。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~I don't know what happened to the money. I just wanted to get out with my life.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~我不知道钱在哪里。光顾着埋头逃命了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Haven't been in here since I was a kid. Shit don't change, do it?
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~小时候来过一次就再没来过了。这里还是没有变化啊。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~And just so you know, I am a very serious person.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~而且你也知道，我都很不好惹了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Man. I dunno. But, uhhh, I'd start looking for a new buyer.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~哥们，我不知道。但是...你最好找个新买家。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~I'm not in the mood for this, Ray. I lost a brother today.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~我没心思谈钱，Ray。我兄弟牺牲了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Unmarked bills! No history, no need to launder.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~干净的钱！没有案底，不需要洗。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, that Niko guy. He's, uhh, in a better place.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~那个，Niko那小子，他...已经去享福了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Got kind of distracted in the Libertonian and, umm, I think the deal's off.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~在博物馆里的时候有点走神了，呃，交易应该是吹了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Scare me on your own then, Johnny.
~z~Okay, guys. Wait here while I get us paid.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~好了，伙计们。在这等我，我去拿钱。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Okay Johnny. Nicky tells me you got away with the money. Bring it to me.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~好了Johnny，Nicky跟我说钱都在你手里。快拿过来。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Then you should cheer up, Raymundo. It didn't feel right. Later.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~那你还是高兴点吧，Raymundo。我觉得有问题。回见。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Niko said that? Dude, that's weird. Shit was kicking off.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~Niko这么说的？老兄，太奇怪了。当时一片混乱。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Thanks for the advice, Ray. I was thinking the same thing about you and a coffin. You got that diamond money?
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~谢谢你的建议，Ray。我觉得你和棺材也挺配的。钻石变现了没？

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~That scene wasn't all that kosher. Call me.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~场面不太符合犹太规矩。再联系吧。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Come back here, you chicken shit motherfuckers.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~回来啊，一群没种的弱鸡玩意！

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~You know I never thought I'd say this, I hope your phone is tapped you fucking imbicile. So long.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~没想到我都能说出这种话，真希望你电话被政府窃听了，你他妈个傻逼。再见。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Terry, man. I need you guys to get down to the Libertonian ASAP. Meet me at the North entrance.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~Terry，哥们，你们赶紧来自由城博物馆。来北门找我。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah. Fuck 'em. I guess we're rich then.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~好，操他妈的。那我们是发财了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~You can bet your balls on it.
~z~Rest of you motherfuckers wanna die - do something stupid okay!
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~哪个狗逼不想活命，就给我动一下试试！

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Ha ha. Yeah, sure. I need some help with an exchange, Terrence.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~哈哈，是这么回事。有笔交易需要你来帮我，Terrence。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Hey, I'm here on behalf of Ray Boccino.
~z~Ray got a contract on me, does he?
~z~You've got to give that girl another chance, you know. You kids are perfect for each other.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~你能不能再给她一次机会啊？其实你俩挺般配的。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~You ain't walking out of here with that cash.
~z~This party ain't over 'til I say it is.
~z~Gentlemen, gentlemen, pardon the precautions. You know how things are.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~先生们，先生们，恕我带了保镖。这年头不安全啊。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Fuck me, these two bums must have hit the jackpot.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~哼，我操，这两个讨饭佬肯定是中大奖了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~The fucking diamonds. Don't let anyone get the diamonds.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~操他妈的钻石。别让别人抢走钻石。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Fuck Ray, man. Fuck all of 'em here.
~z~Where do you think you're going, you little pussies?
~z~Clay, dude, can you and Terry get your asses to the Libertonian? I need some help. I'll see you at the North door, man.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~Clay，老兄，你和Terry赶紧来自由城博物馆。我需要支援。我们北门见，哥们。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~This is a fucking frame up, you damn shysters.
~z~They reminded me too much of you.
~z~Isaac and Mori ain't happy Johnny. I am telling you these are serious people.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~Isaac和Mori很不高兴，Johnny。这些人都不是好惹的。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah? That's real cute. Taking people out is some kind of joke to you?
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~是吗？你真可爱。杀人对你来说就像是玩笑一样吗？

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~You're gonna have to work for it, friend. Hope you don't mind sweating a little.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~这事儿还得你出力，朋友。希望你不介意啊。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~You're not getting the cash, you guido pricks.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~你们拿不到钱了，意大利傻逼。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~You're not getting back to Ray, boys.
~z~Nice tattoos. Your mommy do 'em for you?
~z~James. Where are you, man? I need to give you something.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~James。你在哪呢，哥们？我有东西要给你。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~We had a problem, Raymond. I didn't like the look of some of the muscle at the Libertonian.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~我们有麻烦了，Raymond。博物馆里有些打手的臭脸让我很不爽。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~You start touching them exhibits. Shit. We're coming.
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~你对展品下手了？妈的。我们来了。

E1R2AUD.original: ~z~Ray tell you to jump me, did he?
~z~What's this I hear about you backing out on this deal?
E1R2AUD.translated: ~z~我怎么听说你小子还没交易就跑了？
